Set names on `tbl_now` class

names-set-.tbl_now.Rd

If the modifying the names invalidates the `tbl_now` object the subsetting will return a data frame with the other attributes of the class preserved.

Usage

# S3 method for class 'tbl_now'
names(x) <- value

Arguments

x

an R object.

value

a character vector of up to the same length as x, or NULL.

Value

A `tbl_now` object or a `data.frame`
